{
  "stem": "21786.9",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the drivers came out and he says, oh, my god, you look-- but try to walk into Theresien, for if we take you, you will have to stay in the quarantine camp, and that may take you a few weeks to be free.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Try to walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we just couldn't-- couldn't get it, you know, what is happening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That it happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they have seen these haggard there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] for.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were probably not the only ones who came, I mean, there on trains and similar.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were gathering there prisoners already for-- for a few days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had ordered a quarantine camp, and there was really-- the International Red Cross was in Theresien.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we marched.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we came to this barrier, and there was the casino, which I mentioned, with the gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there is the gendarmes stand-- standing at the-- kind of this thing or this barrier.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The rod which is put across the road.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he says to us, in German, halt!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in German, sit down and wait.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my friend, George Wassermann, is-- we are sitting there quite stunned, realizing that there is no SS.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There is only the gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we look at the building, and on the building there are two flags hanging.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there is-- it's lit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it's a bad lighting, but still light.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I see a white flag with a red cross, and next to it is a white, red, with a blue triangle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A flag of former Czechoslovakia, which was-- I mean, it was automatic arrest and automatic concentration camp to show it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I looked at the gendarme, and on his hat-- cap, on his hood, he has got a little tricolor with the Czechoslovak flag.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
